'''''Red Scorpion''''' ni film muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1988 yakinnye na Dolph Lundgren kandi iyobowe na Joseph Zito . Lundgren agaragara nk’ingabo zidasanzwe z’Abasoviyeti zoherejwe kwica umuyobozi w’inyeshyamba zirwanya abakomunisiti muri [[Afurika]], gusa ashyigikiye inyeshyamba. yakozwe na lobbyist Jack Abramoff kandi yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo yuburengerazuba]] ku nkunga ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo yo muri]] apartheid. Iyi filime yasohotse muri [[Amerika]] ku ya 21 Mata 1989. 

== Umugambi ==
Liyetona Nikolai Petrovitch Rachenko, umukozi wa Spetsnaz w’Abasoviyeti yoherejwe mu gihugu cya [[Afurika]] aho ingabo [[Burusiya|z’Abasoviyeti]], [[Silovakiya|Cekosolovakiya]] na Cuba zifasha guverinoma kurwanya umutwe w’inyeshyamba zirwanya abakomunisiti. Ashinzwe ubutumwa bwo kwica umuyobozi w'inyeshyamba. Rachenko yinjiye mu mutwe w'inyeshyamba no kugera kure cyane y'intego yari afite, ateza ibibazo mu kabari kabo maze atabwa muri yombi azira imyitwarire idahwitse. Yashyizwe mu kagari kamwe n’umuyobozi wafashwe n’umutwe kandi arizera ko byoroshye guhunga. Amaherezo ageze mu nkambi y'inyeshyamba, ahura no kutizerana n'inyeshyamba. Mwijoro, agerageza kwica umugambi we, ariko inyeshyamba zitizera  ibikorwa bye.

=== Igisubizo gikomeye ===
Kevin Thomas wo mu kinyamakuru ''Los Angeles Times'' yasobanuye ko ari "igitabo gisekeje kizwi cyane", ko nubwo Lundgren afite charisma, bishoboka ko byangiza umwuga we.  Stephen Holden wo mu ''kinyamakuru The New York Times'' yanditse ko physique ya Lundgren ari yo nyenyeri nyayo ya filime, kuko ivuga amarangamutima kuruta uko yakinnye.
